Key Match Events: Nikola Jokic scored 9 points in overtime to secure the win for the Denver Nuggets.
Devin Vassell tipped in a rebound to tie the game at 108 with 14 seconds remaining in regulation.
Post-Match Reflections: Nikola Jokic praised Victor Wembanyama, believing he will be'remembered forever' in the league.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The teams split the home-and-home series on consecutive nights.
Julian Champagnie was 3-for-4 on 3-pointers in the two-game set against Denver.
Others: Zach Collins and Russell Westbrook each received a technical foul in the first quarter after taunting one another.
